{"tid":1446993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要大台呀！仆街！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:13:43.000Z","uid":301394,"like":10,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ace9466b4838fb2f09c40ec9c0ebae7664e6276c","tid":1446993,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:37.000Z","msg":"唔可以再等！要做野啦和理非！<br />\n如果睇完我以下計劃認同嘅<br />\n可唔可以推下?<br />\n<br />\n推過1100我會開TG group (我會自推100)<br />\n邀請各界好手加入<br />\n組織統籌大台 (前題:唔好歧視P牌)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">第一階段: 8月12至20日<br />\n全民覺醒召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">方法: 用傳單、海報、air drop 等等</span><br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n喚醒港人721記憶<br />\n提醒解放軍、公安已混入香港<br />\n811爆眼女生<br />\n811克警扮勇武，無恥至極<br />\n政府放任警鄉黑合作治港<br />\n<br />\n所有野係因為政府無能管治香港！<br />\n所有野都係因為無雙選！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n第二階段: 8 月 21 日<br />\n全民請假奔喪 哀悼元朗721事件</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n方法: 全世界請假著白色衫集會默哀<br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n請假令奴性重市民容易接受<br />\n悼念已死嘅公義<br />\n悼念已死嘅香港警察(香港警察已經死晒，得返渣滓，公安進場)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">第三階段: 8 月 22 日 至 8 月 31 日<br />\n全民撳錢轉走MPF放中資股</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n方法: <br />\n去銀行排隊提取所有存款<br />\n轉晒所有MPF 去非中資股票<br />\n放晒所有中資股票<br />\n<br />\n重點:<br />\n香港已陷人道災難<br />\n政治環境非常動盪<br />\n經濟前景唔明朗<br />\n為求自保全民撳錢旁身<br />\n<br />\n你怕股票蝕? 個女仔無左隻眼啦仆街！<br />\n迫政府表態！出黎解決問題！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>第四階段: 9月1日開始</strong></span><br />\n正苦仲唔做野。。。<br />\n我屌佢老母全民大罷工罷課罷市直至世界末日啦屌佢老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">要做到以上嘅野<br />\n係需要一個統籌大台呀仆街<br />\n真係要有組織有計劃<br />\n所有野都冇犯法(法律?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔撚係政治左膠大台<br />\n係和理非統籌大台！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n要大台呀！要文宣呀！要安排人手呀！要計劃呀！仲要搵人課金呀！<br />\n<br />\n係時候和理非要進化啦仆街！</span>"},{"pid":"acd3516f83d1098826d8bd1eee32bf19a271f3c5","tid":1446993,"uid":83019,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"唔要大台"},{"pid":"840f89150abc40a49176b03b4ba9c44c8fa2887b","tid":1446993,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"on撚9"},{"pid":"2a43d9ca72a94e203777a592f3f810eac20f3f90","tid":1446993,"uid":200971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老母就開大台</span></span>"},{"pid":"73010fa0736e144ced20e101d86daf8308216426","tid":1446993,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"acd3516f83d1098826d8bd1eee32bf19a271f3c5","tid":1446993,"uid":83019,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"唔要大台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"睇完先覆啦屌你"},{"pid":"c0fd92acacf5cc0ce93a2e37758512828bc6a373","tid":1446993,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"840f89150abc40a49176b03b4ba9c44c8fa2887b","tid":1446993,"uid":90601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:06.000Z","msg":"on撚9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"睇完先覆呀屌你"},{"pid":"441593872a1463faa6583d22ebfb357a7eb06ced","tid":1446993,"uid":301394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a43d9ca72a94e203777a592f3f810eac20f3f90","tid":1446993,"uid":200971,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老母就開大台</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:30:53.000Z","msg":"睇完先覆呀仆街"},{"pid":"f48a01db944686afce6f3cb841aafb22310689ae","tid":1446993,"uid":272153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"